==桌面软件==
Mac (macOS) 专用的 Cameleon 是该公司相当热门的直播流軟體，近期也推出了 Windows 和 iOS 版本。軟體支持内建有线和无线录像机、高清现场直播流和连接高达 6 台录像机<ref name="Kickstarter">{{Cite web|url=https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/yatko/facebook-live-and-youtube-live-streaming-with-came|title=Facebook Live & YouTube Live Streaming app Cameleon 2.0|accessdate=2016-12-17|work=Kickstarter|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121072839/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/yatko/facebook-live-and-youtube-live-streaming-with-came|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kickstarter2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/yatko/cameleon-your-live-video-channel|title=Cameleon ► Your Live Video Channel|accessdate=2016-12-17|work=Kickstarter|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121072836/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/yatko/cameleon-your-live-video-channel|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

